The paper deals with natural scene text recognition using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of synthetic data and artificial neural networks also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses different ways of encoding words, which is related to natural language processing (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
